Greetings,

We currently have two Teamwork accounts and I am hoping that you can offer us a non-profit discount.

Our accounts are ymcaofpierceandkitsapcountiesmarketing and ymcapkc.

Our non-profit documentation is attached.

Thank you in advance for your response!

Best,

Rachel VanArendonk

Rachel VanArendonk (Maurer)  |  Senior Marketing and Communications Director
YMCA OF PIERCE AND KITSAP COUNTIES

ASSOCIATION OFFICE | 4717 S 19th St Ste 201, Tacoma WA 98405

P 253-534-7847

ymcapkc.org | facebook.com/ymcapkc | twitter.com/ymcapkc

The Y is for youth development, healthy living, and social responsibility.

"

Hello,

Our company is considering purchasing project management software for our team. I was wondering if it would be possible to get a 30 minute demo of Teamwork PM’s capabilities. We are looking for a reasonably priced

alternative that is easy to use, safe and secure, and offers collaboration tools, document management, and if possible, reporting options.

Thank you very much for your time.

Sincerely,

Michèle

M. Streeter, RN, BSN, MS

Director, Clinical Informatics

National Association of Community Health Centers

7501 Wisconsin Avenue

Suite 1100W

Bethesda, MD 20814

Office: 301-347-0453

Cell: 301-310-2833

Fax: 301-347-0459

For more information, visit www.nachc.org.

NACHC, Community

Health Centers and Community HealthCorps are on Facebook.  NACHC is on Twitter

"

Hi there,

I just want to confirm what time the webinar will be taking place for our team tomorrow? During the webinar booking, i selected 9am MST (our time), however, the confirmation email here is saying 4pm? We are located in Calgary, Alberta Canada. Our account can be found at https://stormdivision.teamwork.com

Any light you can shed on this would be appreciated.

Cheers,

Ashley
"
